{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_13_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日の養成所の講師の話だけど\nやっぱりお断りさせてもらおうと思うの",
      "startTime": 5.333333373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロの養成所の子なら、同じ養成所出身の\nリズノワやトリエルから教わった方が嬉しいはずよ",
      "startTime": 12.833333373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.6666667222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、講師をするなら私じゃなくて\n莉央さんや瑠依ちゃんが適任だと思う",
      "startTime": 20.3666667063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしても嫌なら無理強いはしませんが……\n何かやるのを避けたい理由があるんですか？",
      "startTime": 26.3666667063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.1895239113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "……実は私、アイドルを目指していた頃に、バンプロの\n養成所のオーディションを受けたことがあるのよ",
      "startTime": 35.0895238954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "結果は一次審査で落選……アイドルに向いてないって\nはっきり言われたようで、あの時は落ち込んだわ",
      "startTime": 43.6895238954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.1895239113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに向いていないと言われたから\n講師をやることに引け目を感じるということですか",
      "startTime": 50.933333373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.6155555008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "だって、養成所から才能がないと見限られた私が\n同じ養成所で講師をするなんておかしいでしょ？",
      "startTime": 59.4822221516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、実際にオーディションを受けたから分かるの\nバンプロの養成所は入るだけでも大変な狭き門よ",
      "startTime": 68.7488888183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4488888341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "あそこに通えるのは、選ばれた一握りの天才……\n生まれ持った才能とスター性を備えた金の卵だけよ",
      "startTime": 79.133333373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "そんな才能溢れる子達の講師に\n才能がないと言われ続けた私は不釣り合いだわ",
      "startTime": 87.8155534504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.7488867996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺はそうは思いません！　遙子さんは\n自分で思っているより遙かに凄い、特別なアイドルです",
      "startTime": 94.3191248562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.5928776023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってくれるのは嬉しいけど、底辺アイドルだった\n私から期待の新人に教えられることなんて何もないわ",
      "startTime": 103.7262109198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、遙子さんにしか伝えられないことがあるはずです\nだから先方も講師に指名したんじゃないでしょうか",
      "startTime": 113.0666646718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.1234220104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん\n講師の話、もう少しだけ考えてみませんか？",
      "startTime": 117.3999980051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "私にしか伝えられない何か……\nそんなものが本当にあるのかしら",
      "startTime": 126.5174124794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の午後",
      "startTime": 130.4085011081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 131.9507458128
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 131.9507458128
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？　事務所にいないと思ったら\nこんな所で何をしているんですか？",
      "startTime": 136.3999974965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}君……\nちょっと一人で考え事をしていたのよ",
      "startTime": 141.2828999595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 144.3829091307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "底辺アイドルだった私が、バンプロの練習生に\n教えられることはなんなのか……",
      "startTime": 148.0828999595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "私の経験談と言っても\n握手会をしても誰も並んでくれなかったとか……",
      "startTime": 153.7828999595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 157.8495757974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "フェスで歌っても誰も足を止めてくれなかったとか\nライブバトルは連戦連敗で目も当てられなかったとか",
      "startTime": 163.5162332929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "台風直撃の日に野外で誰もいない客席に向かって\n歌ったとか、そんな夢のない話聞きたくないでしょ？",
      "startTime": 173.0162332929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 179.0829091307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "夢がなくてもいいじゃないですか\nなんの苦労もなく売れるほどアイドルは甘くありません",
      "startTime": 181.8333308298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "何度も壁にぶつかって、乗り越えてきた人だけが\nトップアイドルになれるんです",
      "startTime": 188.6666641632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 190.7009139295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そのことを一番よく分かっているのは\n誰よりも苦労してきた遙子さんじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 193.1666641632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに向いてないと言われ続けた私が\nどんな想いで、どれだけ頑張ってきたか……",
      "startTime": 200.7027782833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 205.2027772819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "そんな私の経験が新人の参考になるの？\n私のやってきたことが後輩のお手本に……",
      "startTime": 210.1027681107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "長年の努力が報われて、遙子さんは大勢から慕われ\n沢山の人達に愛されるアイドルになりました",
      "startTime": 220.0333348988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 223.6634431754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに多くの人から愛されている遙子さんが\nアイドルのお手本に向いていないはずがありません",
      "startTime": 226.7000097035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_02-hrk019.m4a",
